%description:
Verify that if a folder listed in cppSourceRoots doesn't exist, it causes an error.

%file: .oppfeatures
<features cppSourceRoots="src bogus"/>

%file: testscript.sh
mkdir -p src
opp_featuretool list

%testprog: sh ./testscript.sh

%exitcode: 1

%contains: stderr
opp_featuretool: Consistency check failed: C++ source folder 'bogus' defined in '.oppfeatures' does not exist

